Italtile Names Ravazzotti as Executive Chairman After His CEO Son's Death

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-02-14T08:08:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-14/italtile-names-ravazzotti-as-executive-chairman-after-his-ceo-son-s-death.html
  Italtile Ltd . said G.A.M. Ravazzotti
was appointed executive chairman of the company after the death
last week of his son and Chief Executive Officer Gianpaolo
Ravazzotti in a plane crash.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
